_sText: This is kinda small map, dusty stylized. Gameplay is fast, but still there are a lot of places to hide. It's hard to stay still and observe the whole map. There is one bug i have found, but, well, it's final. (if you got problems with cubemaps, type "buildcubemaps" in console and restart game/server) I think that's it. If anybody wants, i'll give a link to the.vmf file.
